	(_S_destroy_c_locale): Move checks against _S_c_locale here.
	* config/locale/gnu/c_locale.h: Add _GLIBCPP_NUM_CATEGORIES macro.
	* config/locale/gnu/ctype_members.cc: Simplify _S_destroy_c_locale
