	(__timepunct<_CharT>::_M_put_helper): Same.
	(moneypunct<_CharT, _Intl>::_M_initialize_moneypunct): Same.

	* include/bits/fstream.tcc (filebuf::underflow): Remove
	__codecvt_type typedef.
	(filebuf::_M_convert_to_external): Same.

